data.description: Offer Deadline 1/29 @11am. Move-in ready & modernly updated ranch home in a desirable neighborhood. Spacious kitchen w/ newly added dishwasher, stainless appliances, flooring, quartz countertops and backsplash. Light-filled living room w/ fireplace, original hardwood floors and sliding glass door to covered back deck w/ fully fenced large backyard. Primary bedroom & two additional bedrooms. Fully updated full and half bathrooms w/ brand new tub, shower, glass roller doors, toilets and vanity's.  Finished basement w/ custom bar, tons of storage and spacious laundry room. Attached one car garage w/ new garage door off of newly paved driveway and fresh landscaping. Newer furnace, ac, and windows complete this well built brick home. Walking distance to Albert Schweitzer Elementary School.
